rComments: Good prof. Brightspace very well organized. Flexible and nice. She really care about her students.

Really good prof, weekly quizzes make you stay up to date and you can retake it to boost the mark! Her online lectures are very good, she engage us with survey or in the chat all the time. Super interesting material. The semester is well organized, 3 weeks new material conclude by a fun mini project. Projects are easy but she expect perfection!!

Professor Fenech is not a good lecturer, but she is very caring. She made a well organized online class that was amongst the best I've had. Most of the material came from Youtube videos, but they were high quality and better than the videos she made herself. There was a lot of little quizzes and plenty of homework, but they were graded fairly.
